choices.text: Group Work. My school is small so it isn’t a common problem and is often a hassle for me since I do not work well with other people. Also, it’s amazing what a simple question and aid will do. I feel like when you ask college students what their problem most of the time is, there are numerous variations of “Expenses;” which if you think about it can be really helped by outside organizations. In general, my biggest problem in the work field is going to be people and its because I am going to be dealing with people and animals. Animals because of my major, Zoology and People because in my business summer program, University of California- Berkeley captured my book. Although my first interview had nothing to do with what I would be doing, the presenter did ask me what my biggest weakness was and what I do with it. Realizing that I focus too much on my own performances; especially with people. I also felt the need to be a perfectionist and try over and over to fix my mistake if it even was one. Also, working with the animals; using them to learn facial recognition in Psychology studies to teaching them phrases that have human connotations. I will be “communicating” with one another. Despite it being soft science, Psychology has similarities with Biology and my professor who is a zoologist.
